          <div style={{ fontSize:12, padding:"8px 12px", background:"rgba(255,255,255,0.04)", borderRadius:8, borderLeft:"3px solid #2196F3" }}>🍎 <b style={{color:COLORS.text}}>iPhone (Safari):</b> Tap AA in address bar → Translate to…</div>
